            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Small teams use Airtable, Notion, or Google Sheets. Mid-market teams use Trello, Asana, or ClickUp with content-brief templates. Large teams use dedicated content platforms like CoSchedule, Contently, or Kapost with workflow, approvals, and analytics baked in.</p></div></div>
          </div>
